parameters: That's right! With this, we can make the perfect Flower Crown...!
Um, um...? There's something I want to ask Lunaroa...
Um...? Well...! When we grow up...
When we grow up... what will happen...?
Sure! I want to marry Laura too!

But Papa said that you can only get married if you're a man and a
woman...

I heard it from the traveling poet! In the country called
Yurishin, girls can marry each other too!
Is that so? Then it's okay! Yeah! I'll marry Laura!

Yay! So, which one of us will be the bride? Luna, which one do
you prefer?

Laura can choose! Um...! Oh! How about the taller one becomes the
bride and the smaller one becomes the wife?
Oh no...! What if I don't grow at all...?

I... I have to go to the magic academy starting next year... I
won't be able to come back for five years...

It's okay! I'll wait forever! I'll wait for Luna until she
becomes amazing and comes back!

Really...? If that much time passes... will you forget about
me...? Will you not dislike me...?

There's no way that would happen! I'll always love you! I'll wait
for you forever!
So please don't say things like that... Waaahhh!!

Ah... Don't cry, Laura... But thank you... I was a little
worried... I... I'm going... Please wait for me, okay?
...Yeah! When you come back, let's get married, okay?
Got it! It's a promise, okay!

...I know! Since Luna loves reading books, I'll make a bookmark
that you can use over there!
(I wonder if Luna still remembers the promise...?)

(I'm a little scared... \! But more than that... I want to meet
you... \! And talk...)
When we were little, Luna and... me...?
Um, um...? There's something I want to ask Luna...
Um...? Well... When we grow up...
Sure! I want to marry Laura too!

(Ah... This is from before Luna went to school... It's been 5
years already... The past...)

But Papa said that you can only get married if it's between a man
and a woman...

I heard from the traveling poet! In the country called Yurishin,
girls can marry each other now!
Is that so? Then it's okay! Yes! I will marry Laura!
(I see... I have to tell Luna right away! The poet told me...)

Yay! So, which one of us will be the bride? Luna, which one do
you prefer?

Laura can choose! ...Ah! How about the taller one becomes the
bride and the smaller one becomes the wife?
Oh no...! What if I don't grow at all...?

(Did I... say something like that...? I didn't grow much taller,
so maybe I'm the smaller one.)

I... I have to go to the magic academy starting next year... So I
won't be able to come back for 5 years...

It's okay! I'll wait forever! I'll wait until Luna becomes
amazing and comes back!

Really...? If that much time passes... will you forget about me?
Will you not like me anymore?

(There's no way that would happen. Even now... I love you so
much...)

There's no way that would happen! I'll always love you! I'll wait
forever!
So please don't say things like that... Waaahhh!!

Ah... Don't cry, Laura... But thank you... I was a little
worried... I'm going now... Please wait for me, okay?
(I used to be a crybaby... Luna often comforted me...)
Yeah! Then, let's get married when you come back!

...I know! Luna, since you love reading books, I'll make a
bookmark that you can use over there!
(I wonder if Luna still remembers... the promise?)

(I'm a little scared... but more than that... I want to meet...
and talk...)
